|ID|OPERATOR           |NAME        |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-----------------------------------------------------------
|0 |HASH GROUP BY      |            |1       |6           |
|1 |└─HASH JOIN        |            |1       |5           |
|2 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|t2(idx_str2)|1       |3           |
|3 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN|t1          |1       |3           |
===========================================================
